description: This file is the entry point for a React application, importing core React libraries, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component. It creates a root element using ReactDOM and renders the App component within React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the React component tree into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM.
